{"tid":1320783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[721前夕] [一星期戰役]  勇武+和理非+文宣 大方向   快入！！！","createTime":"2019-07-15T13:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T04:10:48.000Z","uid":231905,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"f039262e3df0291cd9b99f71dd773ee6949e278b","tid":1320783,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:06:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黎緊一星期係比我地儲氣用，大家千祈唔好放軟手腳！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">文宣部同事</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n1. 瘋狂分化藍衫同白衫，高層，聰哥甚至林鄭，出面咁多藍衫叫春post其實有潛力改造成分化材料，唔好淨係po連登！要靠大家努力廣傳出去，目的要推到721有警察罷工，只要有人帶頭罷工黑警一定出事，就算唔罷工都搞到佢地軍心渙散!<br />\n<br />\n2. 宣揚黑警暴行，保護抗爭者光環！目的要社會輿論都要撐示威者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">和理非朋友</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n1. 721一定要靠大家撐人數！人數就是力量已經有好多post講過，大家都明。和理非唔需要衝唔需要受傷，只需要製造聲勢，製造人群保護勇武。<br />\n<br />\n2. 物質支援，前線好多人都係學生，未必有咁多錢買裝備，和理非朋友可以準備物資支援，做後勤，買多一個頭盔就少一個人爆缸<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">勇武派</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n呢個星期好好購物啦<br />\n1. 最最最重要要買Gas Mask!!! 次次一出Gas我地就潰不成軍。前線一定要準備好mask，起碼要有幾十人頂到gas先形成到戰鬥力。<br />\nP.s. 我有個fd仲成9日話唔洗啦乜乜77，大佬呀你唔衝，走佬都要啦下話？係咪未撚食過gas唔識驚呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3200 + 3311係經濟型，100$內有一set<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OBP9MCP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBP9MCP.jpg&h=2963bcbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6字頭雙嘴型就高級版，有預算可以買<br />\n要過濾有機氣體+p100就最安全<br />\n<br />\n2. 長短火<br />\n長火係比大家對峙用，唔比狗埋身，捅返佢兩野，傘陣除左擋椒都可免則免，捲埋當長兵器用仲實際 ikea遮有巴打post過啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s8a1CKi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs8a1CKi.jpg&h=22373256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n短火係狗仔落單用，咁好渣手，相信唔洗多解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZytiEXH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZytiEXH.jpg&h=da573756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 護身裝甲<br />\n頭唔撚洗講，幾多人爆缸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手甲都好重要，擋棍通常靠前臂，但係就難買d<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kv0thKq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkv0thKq.jpg&h=2895fc60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之多一樣就再安全d，多左裝個人安全感多左，衝都衝得勁d<br />\n<br />\n721 武運昌隆"},{"pid":"4ebb4b986296e72eebc0f10580d82c1bdc83e387","tid":1320783,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:06:48.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2399886bb31e10843c7ca3b27d23b43797438494","tid":1320783,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"cd341d9c5d8effb3130f95b19d19952979ded405","tid":1320783,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:08:38.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d8955057e6505025cc028dc2dab9f02c5ba4f4fc","tid":1320783,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:09:29.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4d7473bd79bcc909c8f176eb8a524e3bdac77c96","tid":1320783,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:10:21.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e808adb7d6c2d60362099186f4a4e2cb233c9555","tid":1320783,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:11:01.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"700d2901892728d20b115697b859709afa5ad98f","tid":1320783,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:11:37.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pi